    {
      "id": "body.index.p.2",
      "en": "Elemento lets you build and run your own cloud infrastructure with complete freedom. You choose where it runs and we automate everything for you. Your cloud. Your rules, Your freedom.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.20",
      "en": "Modernize legacy applications with minimal disruption. Migrate to cloud-native architecture while maintaining compliance and security. Define your rules for governance and enjoy the freedom to choose your cloud strategy. Support for hybrid and multi-cloud strategies.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.21",
      "en": "Streamline CI/CD pipelines with infrastructure as code. Deploy faster with automated provisioning and monitoring. Integrate with existing tools and workflows seamlessly.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.22",
      "en": "Accelerate machine learning workflows with GPU-optimized infrastructure. Scale compute resources on-demand and manage data pipelines efficiently across multiple environments.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.23",
      "en": "Deploy applications globally with edge computing capabilities. Reduce latency and improve user experience with intelligent workload distribution across 235+ data centers.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.24",
      "en": "Meet strict regulatory requirements with compliance-ready infrastructure. Deploy in sovereign regions with end-to-end encryption and comprehensive audit trails.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.25",
      "en": "See how organizations are transforming their cloud infrastructure with Elemento",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.26",
      "en": "Join hundreds of organizations that have revolutionized their cloud operations with Elemento. Learn about our company mission and explore our product solutions .",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.27",
      "en": "Everything you need to know about Elemento Cloud Platform.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.28",
      "en": "Elemento is a vendor-neutral cloud platform that abstracts away the differences between cloud providers. Unlike traditional providers that lock you into their ecosystem, Elemento gives you a unified interface to deploy and manage workloads across AWS, Azure, Google Cloud, and your own infrastructure. This means you can move workloads freely without rewriting applications or changing your deployment processes.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.29",
      "en": "Customers typically save 60-80% on cloud costs through intelligent workload placement, real-time pricing optimization, and the ability to run workloads on your own hardware. Elemento enables real-time arbitrage across cloud providers and can automatically move workloads to the most cost-effective infrastructure while maintaining performance and reliability.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.3",
      "en": "Loading trusted companies...",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.30",
      "en": "Elemento provides bank-grade security with end-to-end encryption, compliance-ready architecture, and the ability to run in your own data center for maximum control. We support SOC 2, GDPR, and industry-specific compliance requirements. All data is encrypted in transit and at rest, with optional customer-managed encryption keys. Learn more about our security and compliance features .",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.31",
      "en": "Yes! Elemento supports migration from existing cloud providers and on-premises infrastructure. Our platform is compatible with standard virtualization technologies and container platforms. We provide migration tools and support to help you move workloads with minimal downtime. Most applications require no code changes.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.32",
      "en": "We provide comprehensive documentation, video tutorials, and a knowledge base. Enterprise customers get dedicated support with SLAs, while community users can access our active community forum and GitHub repositories. We also offer training programs and workshops for teams.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.33",
      "en": "Elemento offers a generous free tier that includes up to 2 VMs on AtomOS, basic Electros features, and access to Atomosphere API. This is perfect for testing, development, and small projects. You can upgrade to paid plans anytime for additional features, support, and higher usage limits.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.34",
      "en": "Yes! Elemento fully supports Kubernetes and container workloads. You can deploy and manage Kubernetes clusters across any cloud provider, and our platform provides additional orchestration capabilities on top of Kubernetes. We also support Docker containers, Helm charts, and other container-native tools.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.35",
      "en": "Elemento supports 235+ data centers worldwide across all major cloud providers. This includes AWS regions, Azure regions, Google Cloud regions, and numerous edge locations. You can deploy workloads in any region and easily move them between regions for optimal performance and compliance. Explore our deployment options and global infrastructure .",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.4",
      "en": "We unify all Clouds into a universal platform that gives you freedom of choice, the best prices and the flexibility to move seamlessly between public and private Clouds. With Elemento, you set your rules for how your infrastructure operates, ensuring complete freedom from vendor lock-in. Learn more about our mission and values or explore our complete product suite .",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.5",
      "en": "Full portability of workloads across any cloud provider",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.6",
      "en": "Deploy workloads quickly on public or private clouds",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.7",
      "en": "Manage all resources from a single interface or via CLI - your rules, your way",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.8",
      "en": "Assemble and scale VMs, storage, and networking as needed",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "index.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.index.p.9",
